{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Live, then Autopanic.</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is <i>Autopanic Zero</i>?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Autopanic Zero is a minimalist twinstick shooter survival game with deep customizability to multiple playstyle. Designed with quick sessions in mind.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The balance is carefully crafted to be quite challenging which might not suit everyone, but completely beatable even with the starting gear.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What isn't\u00a0<i>Autopanic Zero</i>?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is <strong>not</strong> really a Vampire Survival-like. At least I don't think so.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is <strong>not</strong> an auto battler, you can try to play like one but it's not really balanced around it.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A variety of abilities and weapons for you to combine and dominate the fast-paced combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carefully balanced gameplay that will greatly challenge your shooting skills as much as your overall strategizing. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Quick ten minute loop for a more busy age.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minimalist visual style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tons of unlockable parts to customize your gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Created by one person.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ground Zero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1423670/6908bad73448bcce3a27b446342876cae3ff36e8.jpg"}],"total":1},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732247600","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423670/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732247600","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.